PGP INFO
--------

If you've got access to PGP, then make sure that you use the PGP signature
to check the integrity of UltraAccounts *before* using the program. My
public PGP key is below - you'll find my PGP key fingerprint in my on-line
resume on CIX, or just drop me a line and ask for it.

To check the integrity of the UltraAccounts executable, all you have to do
is add my public key to your PGP keyring and then type the following in a
Shell window...

    PGP UltraAccounts.sig UltraAccounts

...and a message will be displayed telling you whether or not it's safe to
use this copy of the program.

Here's my public PGP key:

